flowchart TD
    A[Fetch email from INBOX] --> B{Lookup sender<br/>in exact rules}
    B -->|Match found| D{Rule has<br/>important: true?}
    B -->|No match| C{Evaluate regex<br/>rules in order}
    C -->|Match found| D
    C -->|No match| E[Mark as unknown<br/>Return to Claude<br/>for classification]

    D -->|No| F[Apply action immediately]
    D -->|Yes| G[Flag email ★<br/>Create TTL record<br/>Leave in INBOX]

    F --> H{Action has folder?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Mark read if mark_read<br/>Flag if flag<br/>Move to action folder]
    H -->|No| J[Apply flags only<br/>Stay in current folder]

    G --> K[Email visible in INBOX<br/>for important_ttl_days]
    K --> L[process_ttl_expirations<br/>runs on next session]
    L --> M[Unflag + move to<br/>action folder]

    I --> N[Email triaged ✓]
    J --> N
    M --> N

    style E fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107
    style G fill:#cce5ff,stroke:#007bff
    style N fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
